item.title: Welcome to the Blog; preamble & Milk & Bone - Hands Dirty Analysis
item.description: Preamble The Vibee: Hands Dirty Artist: Milk & Bone Welcome, this is my first attempt at writing one of these ‘blogs’ Lol. I tend to write how I think, speak and generally view data and information. If you know me, you know how sarcastic and melancholy I can be. I express myself heavily through music, lyrics, when I don’t have the words, music speaks on my behalf. If you’ve followed me on Twitter, Bluesky, or anything really, since I was a kid I’ve always shared music to sort of communicate my inner-world to the outside world.
